productName: Weston Wireless Charging Power Bank Stand & Speaker
description: The Weston Wireless Charging Powerbank Stand & Bluetooth Speaker delivers premium sound with built in power! The 3Watt speaker driver of the Weston Bluetooth Speaker provide enough volume to be heard across the room. While you’re playing your favorite audio or watching a movie place your phone on the front of the speaker and tap the front panel to deliver a wireless charge to your device. Please note your phone must be compatible with wireless charging. The Weston Wireless Charging Powerbank also has a built in USB output to provide a charge to your device with the correct cable. Included with the Speaker is a 20” micro USB Cable. The built in microphone and music controls allow you to use the speaker for conference calls or video calls. Playback time at max volume: 5hrs. Charge Time of Speaker: 3hrs. USB Output: 5V/2A. Supports 5Watt Wireless Charging. Battery Capacity: 2500maH. Bluetooth Version 5.0

It also features wireless charging at up to 1A for devices including (but not limited to ): iPhone 8/8Plus/X/XS/XS Max/XR/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max *Samsung Galaxy Note5/S6/S6 Edge/S6 Edge+/S7/S7 Edge/S8/S8+/S9/S9+/Note 9 * Google Nexus 5/6/7 * HTC Droid DNA  8X * LG G3/G4  Lucid 2/3 * Nokia Lumia 920/930 *. If want to charge a phone without wireless technology  an external Qi-standard wireless charging receiver or receiver case is required. This device will work with any smartphone that does not have wireless technology through the normal power bank capabilities. Includes a Micro USB to USB charging cable which can recharge the power bank or can be used to charge up devices with a Micro USB input like Android Smartphones from Samsung?  and others. Input 5V/1A  output 5V/1A. It works with most plastic phone cases on.
